    if request.user.is_authenticated:
        item =get_object_or_404(Item, slug=slug)
        order_item,created =OrderItem.objects.get_or_create(item =item,user =request.user ,ordered =False)

        if order_qs.exists():
            order =order_qs[0]

                order_item.quantity += 1
                order_item.save()
